videos.description: Texas freshman Jaxson Hayes slips past Kansas defenders and slams home a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Hayes gets up 2-handed flush

videos.headline: Garrett spins in for tough layup

videos.headline: Texas misses game-winning 3-pointer
